# MVVM 架构规范

## 层级职责

```
UI (Fragment) → ViewModel → Repository → DataSource (Room/API)
```

| 层级 | 职责 | 禁止 |
|------|------|------|
| UI | 展示数据、响应用户操作 | 业务逻辑、数据获取 |
| ViewModel | 管理 UI 状态、处理用户意图 | 直接操作数据库、网络 |
| Repository | 数据聚合、缓存策略 | 业务决策 |
| DataSource | 数据读写 | 业务逻辑 |

## ViewModel 模式

```kotlin
class MyViewModel @Inject constructor(
    private val repository: MyRepository
) : ViewModel() {

    // 私有可变状态
    private val _state = MutableStateFlow<MyState>(MyState.Init)

    // 公开不可变状态
    val state: StateFlow<MyState> = _state.asStateFlow()

    // 用户动作
    fun onAction(action: MyAction) {
        when (action) {
            is MyAction.Load -> loadData()
            is MyAction.Refresh -> refresh()
        }
    }

    private fun loadData() {
        viewModelScope.launch {
            repository.getData().collect { resource ->
                _state.value = when (resource) {
                    is Resource.Loading -> MyState.Loading
                    is Resource.Success -> MyState.Success(resource.data)
                    is Resource.Error -> MyState.Error(resource.message)
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
```

## 状态类设计

```kotlin
// UI 状态
sealed class MyState {
    data object Init : MyState()
    data object Loading : MyState()
    data class Success(val data: List<Item>) : MyState()
    data class Error(val message: String) : MyState()
}

// 用户动作
sealed class MyAction {
    data object Load : MyAction()
    data object Refresh : MyAction()
    data class Select(val id: String) : MyAction()
}
```

## Fragment 绑定

```kotlin
class MyFragment : Fragment() {

    private var _binding: FragmentMyBinding? = null
    private val binding get() = _binding!!

    private val viewModel: MyViewModel by viewModels()

    override fun onViewCreated(view: View, savedInstanceState: Bundle?) {
        super.onViewCreated(view, savedInstanceState)
        _binding = FragmentMyBinding.bind(view)

        // 收集状态
        viewLifecycleOwner.lifecycleScope.launch {
            viewLifecycleOwner.repeatOnLifecycle(Lifecycle.State.STARTED) {
                viewModel.state.collect { state ->
                    render(state)
                }
            }
        }

        // 设置点击监听
        binding.btnSubmit.setOnClickListener {
            viewModel.onAction(MyAction.Submit)
        }
    }

    private fun render(state: MyState) {
        when (state) {
            is MyState.Loading -> showLoading()
            is MyState.Success -> showData(state.data)
            is MyState.Error -> showError(state.message)
            else -> {}
        }
    }

    override fun onDestroyView() {
        super.onDestroyView()
        _binding = null
    }
}
```

## Flow 收集规则

```kotlin
// ✅ 正确：在 Lifecycle.State.STARTED 时收集
repeatOnLifecycle(Lifecycle.State.STARTED) {
    viewModel.flow.collect { }
}

// ✅ 使用 WhileSubscribed 控制上游发布
val flow = _flow.stateIn(
    viewModelScope,
    SharingStarted.WhileSubscribed(5000),
    initialValue
)

// ❌ 避免在 launchIn 中使用，可能导致内存泄漏
// ❌ 避免在 onCreate 中直接 launch
```
